data.description: So much character in this 3 bedroom home! Welcoming you to the home is a large covered front porch that takes you into the home with beautiful hardwood floors. Into the dining room you have original built-ins for extra storage. Taking you to the carpeted upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms and a full bathroom, with access to the attic from the bathroom. Enjoy your backyard on your newly built deck, firepit and garden. The large two car detached garage is perfect for your vehicles or additional space. Come see this adorable home today!!
